# PVCasa Catalog Web Application

## Overview

PVCasa is a web application designed for product catalog management, organized into two main areas: a client interface for users and an admin panel for managing products and access.

## Features

### Client
- Browse and view products
- Search and apply filters

### Admin
- Create, edit, and delete products
- Authentication system for secure access

## Tech Stack

- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Firebase (Authentication and Database)
- Nginx (routing)

## Project Structure

- `client/` — user-facing catalog interface
- `admin/` — product management and authentication system

## Status

In progress
